STATE of North Carolina
v.
Camellia BROWN No. 353P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 26, 2016 Ms. Camellia Boyd Norton Brown, for Brown, Camellia Boyd Norton. Ms. Anne M. Middleton, Special Deputy Attorney General, Ms. N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Ms. Camellia Brown, For Brown, Camellia.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 26th of September 2016 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 26th of September 2016."
